dct_title_s: Gloucester City: Newton Creek to Little Timber Creek
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Newton Creek to Little Timber Creek. Map is primarily showing the road layout of Gloucester City, but it also shows property ownership and proposed bulkhead lines as well as the West Jersey and Seashore Railroad.
